Installation:

git clone git://github.com/oletros/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

Original: http://vimcasts.org/episodes/synchronizing-plugins-with-git-submodules-and-pathogen/
vimrc: https://github.com/spf13/spf13-vim
